The three cute princesses Ariel, Anna and Jasmine have broken up with their love. Yesterday they all were surrounded by the intense sadness. But, today they all have decided to begin a new life. For this purpose, they seek for the new kind of looks. Would you give your helping hands to these cute princesses with broken heart? Join Ex Girlfriend Party game and be prepared to guide them to attain the best-looking outfits! You would have plenty of outfit options to explore in the closet. 
Your primary objective in this brand new dressing game for girls is to make the shopping of these cute princesses a hassle-free experience. They are very positive for their new life and looking forward to get their new looks. These girls do not have as much good fashion sense as you have. So, they have keep faith on your abilities, so play with full of confidence and keep mixing and matching dresses until you design the fabulous design for them. Give her first girl a black and pink one piece, or a white and black color dress!
Adorn your girl with a nice and matching handbag, jewelry and a pair of cute shoes! Once you are done with the look of first girl, move towards the other two princesses who also need your help. After completing the looks of the three girls, click on the next button to see the final results. Good luck to create more fabulous outfit designs in our free online princess dress-up games for kids!
